<li id="cite_note-14"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Milner, Richard (1990). <i>The Encyclopedia of Evolution</i>. NY: Facts on File, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.stephenjaygould.org/biography.html">p. 198.</a></span>
