<li id="cite_note-Spandrels-50"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Spandrels_50-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Spandrels_50-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFGouldLewontin1979" class="citation journal cs1">Gould, S. J.; Lewontin, Richard (1979). "The spandrels of San Marco and the Panglossian paradigm: a critique of the adaptationist programme". <i>Proc. R. Soc. Lond. B Biol. Sci</i>. <b>205</b> (1161): 581–98. <a href="/wiki/Bibcode_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Bibcode (identifier)">Bibcode</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1979RSPSB.205..581G">1979RSPSB.205..581G</a>. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1098%2Frspb.1979.0086">10.1098/rspb.1979.0086</a>. <a href="/wiki/PMID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="PMID (identifier)">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/42062">42062</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:2129408">2129408</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Proc.+R.+Soc.+Lond.+B+Biol.+Sci.&amp;rft.atitle=The+spandrels+of+San+Marco+and+the+Panglossian+paradigm%3A+a+critique+of+the+adaptationist+programme&amp;rft.volume=205&amp;rft.issue=1161&amp;rft.pages=581-98&amp;rft.date=1979&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1098%2Frspb.1979.0086&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A2129408%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F42062&amp;rft_id=info%3Abibcode%2F1979RSPSB.205..581G&amp;rft.aulast=