<li id="cite_note-66"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-66">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFGould1997" class="citation interview cs1">Gould, Jay (January 1997). "Stephen Jay Gould". <i><a href="/wiki/Mother_Jones_(magazine)" title="Mother Jones (magazine)">Mother Jones</a></i> (Interview). Interviewed by <a href="/wiki/Michael_Krasny_(talk_show_host)" title="Michael Krasny (talk show host)">Michael Krasny</a>. San Francisco: Mother Jones Magazine.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Mother+Jones&amp;rft.atitle=Stephen+Jay+Gould&amp;rft.date=1997-01&amp;rft.aulast=Gould&amp;rft.aufirst=Jay&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AStephen+Jay+Gould" class="Z3988"></span></span>
