<li id="cite_note-110"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-110">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFKorb1994" class="citation journal cs1">Korb, Kevin B. (August 1994). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/0010027794900647">"Stephen Jay Gould on intelligence"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Cognition_(journal)" title="Cognition (journal)">Cognition</a></i>. <b>52</b> (2): 111–123. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1016%2F0010-0277%2894%2990064-7">10.1016/0010-0277(94)90064-7</a>. <a href="/wiki/PMID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="PMID (identifier)">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/7924200">7924200</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:10514854">10514854</a><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">December 30,</span> 2022</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Cognition&amp;rft.atitle=Stephen+Jay+Gould+on+intelligence&amp;rft.volume=52&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=111-123&amp;rft.date=1994-08&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A10514854%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F7924200&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1016%2F0010-0277%2894%2990064-7&amp;rft.aulast=Korb&amp;rft.aufirst=Kevin+B.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2F0010027794900647&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AStephen+Jay+Gould" class="Z3988"></span></span>
